Extension : OWMigration v1.1
Requires : eZ Publish 4.x.x (not tested on 3.X)
Author : Open Wide <http://www.openwide.fr>

What is OWMigration?
-------------------

OW Migration provide an API to migrate content class.
 
Usage
------
1. Create a class that extends the class OWMigration.
2. Implement the methods up () and down ().
3. Reload autoloads
4. Run the script migrate.php :
php extension/OWMigration/bin/migrate.php --migration-class=yourMigrationClass --up
or
php extension/OWMigration/bin/migrate.php --migration-class=yourMigrationClass --down

You can see some exemples of migration class in the exemples directory of this extension, or see and export migration class fron back-end.

Enjoy !!


